E%20kick%20in.%20For%20some%2C%20those%20raises%20will%20be%20historic%3A%20In%20six%20states%2C%20the%20minimum%20wage%20will%20reach%20at%20least%20%2415%20an%20hour%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2019%20states%20hiking%20wages%20will%20impact%20over%208%20million%20workers%2C%20an%20analysis%20from%20the%20Economic%20Policy%20Institute%2C%20a%20left-leaning%20think%20tank%2C%20found.%20Women%2C%20Black%2C%20and%20Hispanic%20workers%20are%20set%20to%20be%20disproportionately%20affected%20by%20the%20new%20increases%2C%20per%20EPI's%20analysis%2C%20and%20workers%20in%20states%20like%20Missouri%20and%20Nebraska%20will%20see%20their%20annual%20wages%20increase%20by%20nearly%20%241%2C000%20on%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20map%20below%20shows%20which%20states%20are%20set%20for%20a%20raise%20in%20January%2C%20and%20what%20those%20increases%20will%20be.%20Most%20January%20increases%20are%20due%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-inflation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einflation%20adjustments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20although%20some%20are%20tied%20to%20legislation%20or%20ballot%20measures%2C%20such%20as%20in%20Rhode%20Island%2C%20where%20legislation%20set%20a%20gradual%20increase%20from%20%2415%20in%202025%20to%20%2417%20by%202027.%20The%20minimum%20wage%20there%20will%20reach%20%2416%20on%20January%201%2C%202026.%20A%20few%20states%20will%20hike%20their%20minimum%20wage%20later%20this%20year%3B%20Florida%20will%20increase%20its%20minimum%20by%20a%20dollar%20to%20%2415%20at%20the%20end%20of%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FMCyUk%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Minimum%20wage%20increases%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22357%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20round%20of%20raises%20will%20hit%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20milestone%20for%20the%20minimum%20wage%20movement%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20EPI's%20Sebastian%20Martinez%20Hickey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20really%20distinctive%20is%20that%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20January%2C%20there%20are%20going%20to%20be%20more%20workers%20that%20live%20in%20a%20state%20with%20at%20least%20a%20%2415%20minimum%20wage%20compared%20to%20those%20that%20live%20in%20a%20state%20with%20the%20federal%20minimum%20wage%2C%20which%20is%20still%20%247.25%2C%26quot%3B%20Hickey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20fresh%20round%20of%20statewide%20increases%20means%20an%20even%20greater%20discrepancy%20in%20some%20local%20wages%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-labor-market-federal-minimum-wage-raise-small-business-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20minimum%20wage%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20majority%20of%20states%20have%20stepped%20in%20to%20increase%20their%20pay%20beyond%20the%20federal%20minimum%2C%20although%2020%20states%20still%20either%20mandate%20%247.25%20or%20default%20to%20the%20federal%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYannet%20Lathrop%2C%20a%20senior%20researcher%20and%20policy%20analyst%20at%20the%20National%20Employment%20Law%20Project%2C%20said%20that%20while%20the%20new%20spate%20of%20%2415%20minimum%20wages%20will%20likely%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20many%20%E2%80%94%20and%20reflects%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-workers-fighting-for-15-minimum-wage-for-a-decade-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong%20history%20of%20organizing%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20workers%20will%20still%20contend%20with%20affordability%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20these%20wages%2C%20as%20good%20as%20they%20are%2C%20as%20positive%20as%20they%20are%20for%20workers%2C%20none%20of%20them%20are%20going%20to%20fully%20cover%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20for%20even%20single%20