rd%20a%20Delta%20and%20KLM%20flight%20across%20the%20Atlantic%2C%20the%20entire%20Albuquerque%20Family%20was%20bitten%20and%20injured%20by%20bed%20bugs%20that%20had%20infested%20the%20cabin%20of%20the%20plane%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F26387937-albuquerque-et-al-v-delta-air-lines-inc-et-al%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20claimed%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20that%20the%20bites%20led%20to%20%26quot%3Braised%20and%20itchy%20welts%2C%20lesions%2C%20and%20rashes%20across%20their%20torsos%20and%20extremities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20said%20the%20family%20wishes%20to%20be%20compensated%20for%20the%20incident%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bruined%20their%20family%20vacation%26quot%3B%20and%20caused%20%26quot%3Bembarrassment%2C%20anxiety%2C%20discomfort%2C%20inconvenience%2C%20medical%20expenses%2C%20and%20loss%20of%20clothing%20and%20personal%20items.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Albuquerque's%20took%20a%20Delta%20flight%20from%20Roanoke%20to%20Atlanta%2C%20then%20a%20KLM%20flight%20to%20Amsterdam%2C%20and%20then%20to%20Belgrade%2C%20Serbia%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20The%20family%20had%20planned%20a%20vacation%20to%20Serbia%20to%20visit%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Delta%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20allegations%20at%20issue%20relate%20to%20flights%20not%20operated%20by%20Delta%20Air%20Lines.%26quot%3B%20The%20airline%20added%20that%20it%20will%20%26quot%3Breview%20the%20complaint%20and%20respond%20accordingly%20in%20due%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20states%20the%20flights%20were%20round-trip%20and%20business%20class%2C%20purchased%20through%20Delta's%20SkyMiles%20program%2C%20and%20operated%20by%20KLM.%20The%20four%20tickets%20were%20worth%20%248%2C800%20at%20the%20time%2C%20according%20to%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%20two%20hours%20into%20the%20flight%20to%20Amsterdam%2C%20one%20of%20the%20plaintiffs%20started%20to%20feel%20like%20she%20was%20being%20bitten%20by%20bugs%20crawling%20on%20her%2C%20according%20to%20the%20filing.%20She%20then%20realized%20that%20bugs%20were%20%26quot%3Bcrawling%20on%20her%20light-colored%20sweater%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20claims%20the%20couple%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%26quot%3B%20notified%20the%20flight%20staff%20and%20were%20told%20to%20keep%20their%20voices%20down%20to%20avoid%20causing%20%26quot%3Bpanic%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20plane.%20The%20couple%20took%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20the%20bugs%20crawling%20on%20the%20sweater%20and%20in%20the%20creases%20of%20their%20seats%2C%20which%20were%20included%20in%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20landing%2C%20the%20flight%20attendants%20urged%20the%20couple%20again%20not%20to%20tell%20anyone%20about%20the%20infestation%20because%20they%20would%20miss%20their%20connecting%20flight%20to%20Serbia%20if%20they%20did%2C%20the%20filing%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20little%20over%20a%20week%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20couple%20took%20their%20children%20to%20doctors%20in%20Roanoke%2C%20Virginia%2C%20where%20it%20was%20confirmed%20that%20the%20bites%20were%20caused%20by%20bed%20bugs%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%20The%20family%20was%20recommended%20to%20employ%20%26quot%3Bbug%20bombs%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20home%20and%20car%2C%20and%20wash%20their%20clothing%20in%20hot%20water%2C%20the%20filing%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20bed%20bugs%20are%20an%20unusual%20complaint%2C%20this%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20passengers%20have%20turned%20to%20the%20courts%20after%20a%20bad%20flight%20experience.%20In%20September%2C%2016%20passengers%20sued%20American%20Airlines%20after%20their%20flight%20caught%20fire.%20Last%20year%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-passenger-sues-for-1-million-says-faulty-armrest